item.title: Assalaam Vaalekum lyrics - Aap Kaa Surroor
item.description: Jab Aaye Saamne Nazron Ke Tum Hosh-o-Hawaas Mere Ho Jaaye Gum Duaayein Karoon Main Sajda Karoon Yahi Main..

item.title: Jhoot Nahin Bolna lyrics
item.description: Apni Zulfon Me Meri Ungliyan Rehne Do Apne Honthon Pe Meri Galtiyan Rehne Do Apne Seene Me Meri..

item.title: Tanhaiyan lyrics - Himesh Reshammiya, Sunidhi Chauhan
item.description: Saara Aalam, Saare Mausam Saari Khushiyan, Saari Duniya Tere Bagair..

item.title: Tere Bina lyrics - Aap Kaa Surroor
item.description: Na Meri Saansein Chale Na Mere Palchhin Kate Beete Na Mere Dina Mere Dina… Tere Bina, Tere Bina..

item.title: Kya Jeena lyrics - Himesh Reshammiya
item.description: Tu Hai Jaise Rab Di Meher Kya Jeena, Jeena Kya Jeena Tere Bagair Jeena Mera Kya..

item.title: Tera Mera Milna lyrics - Aap Kaa Surroor
item.description: Yeh Tera Mera Milna Yun Dilon Ka Khilna Yeh Hai Khuda Ki Marzi Yun Hi Nahi Hai..
